text: I attended the opening ceremony of the Moving Wall—a replica of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial—at Mark Coronado Park in Surprise. This tribute to will be open to the public day and night until July 9th at noon. The wall has the names of 58,000 heroes we lost from the Vietnam War. pic.twitter.com/mKDmVDDtGQ
